author: denizoran
text: There is no such term/word as 'OVEREXAGGERATION'. Exaggeration by itself means emphasizing or overdoing something. No offense.

author: Jay Jh
text: cute video , nice song, \nthis wont be enough, its time for ppl to change, and no global warming is NOT beening overexaggerated....\nthese changes can be slowed down, yeh plant more trees, but thats not it, soo much pollution one person cant stop this, everyone has to come together and make a difference, i want my grandkids and they kids to see the polar bears, i want them to have a bright future. we should not only care about today or tomorrow but the years to come...
